WEBVTT

00:33.075 --> 00:34.656
Lotte entertainment presents

00:48.340 --> 00:53.130
between heaven and earth
is a place called cloudland.

00:56.223 --> 01:04.187
People stay until they're forgotten
before going up to heaven.

01:08.318 --> 01:16.318
Mommy penguin peeped down on earth
through a hole and cried everyday.

01:24.209 --> 01:27.542
When the rainy season
started 1 year later,

01:28.046 --> 01:32.335
she secretly hopped on
the raindrop train.

01:39.725 --> 01:42.842
The train stopped
at a small station.

01:43.979 --> 01:48.564
Suddenly, she heard a baby’s cry.

01:50.068 --> 01:55.984
She ran over to find her baby penguin
in a yellow raincoat crying.

02:06.251 --> 02:10.995
She held her baby penguin tight.

02:12.049 --> 02:15.883
Suddenly, a miracle happened!

02:21.725 --> 02:27.470
Mommy and baby
always stayed together.

02:28.190 --> 02:30.101
They played games.

02:31.234 --> 02:36.820
Mommy taught her baby
how to fish, and had fun together.

02:37.824 --> 02:41.066
Soon, the rainy season
was almost over.

02:42.537 --> 02:48.077
Raindrop fairy from cloudland
came and whispered to mommy penguin.

02:49.586 --> 02:55.047
"You must return
before the clouds roll away."

02:56.051 --> 03:00.385
"If you miss the last raindrop train,
you can’t go back to cloudland.”

03:01.890 --> 03:05.883
"then you won't be able to watch
your baby through the clouds.”

03:08.563 --> 03:13.227
mommy was sad, but she didn’t cry.

03:14.236 --> 03:18.400
Her baby smiled back at her too.

03:20.492 --> 03:27.864
They hugged each other
and said goodbye with a smile.

03:28.792 --> 03:31.534
Mommy penguin returned to cloudland

03:31.586 --> 03:38.128
and watched her baby everyday,
but didn’t cry anymore.

03:44.349 --> 03:46.681
70 j-ho from mom

03:47.018 --> 03:48.724
she died way too young.

03:50.063 --> 03:54.557
Can the boy's father
take care of him?

03:54.943 --> 03:59.232
We warned it'd be dangerous
to have a baby.

04:00.323 --> 04:03.190
She was fine
before giving birth.

04:03.452 --> 04:04.908
That's right!

04:09.332 --> 04:11.038
See you again, mom.

04:19.843 --> 04:26.180
Be with you

04:28.393 --> 04:31.556
1 year later
summer, 2006

05:01.176 --> 05:05.010
so j-sub

05:08.058 --> 05:11.767
son ye-Jin

05:14.856 --> 05:18.189
Kim j-hwan, go Chang-suk

05:21.196 --> 05:24.905
Lee you-Jin, Kim hyeon-soo

06:41.151 --> 06:46.271
directed by Lee jang-hoon

07:01.379 --> 07:03.870
ji-ho! Wake up!

07:05.133 --> 07:06.543
It’s time for school!

07:09.554 --> 07:10.554
Son!

07:19.439 --> 07:21.600
Slept in her wardrobe again?

07:26.404 --> 07:28.770
Let's have breakfast.
Wake up!

07:36.247 --> 07:38.738
It’s sunny throughout
the country today.

07:39.000 --> 07:42.037
It'll be a high of 29 °c in Seoul.

07:42.045 --> 07:43.751
Daegu will go up to a high of 30 °c.

07:43.797 --> 07:46.459
It'll be 2~3 degrees hotter
than yesterday.

07:46.466 --> 07:48.957
The rainy season will begin
this weekend.

07:49.260 --> 07:54.550
Jeju island
will get heavy downfalls.

07:54.599 --> 07:57.181
The seasonal rain front
isn’t moving northward...

07:59.229 --> 08:01.311
Does rainy season
start with rain?

08:01.606 --> 08:02.391
Probably.

08:02.440 --> 08:03.771
Does it always rain?

08:06.319 --> 08:07.980
It usually comes and goes.

08:09.614 --> 08:10.854
You said it has to rain.

08:11.700 --> 08:13.406
When rainy season starts,

08:14.202 --> 08:17.444
sometimes it rains
and sometimes it doesn’t.

08:22.794 --> 08:24.284
What if it rains in jeju island?

08:24.462 --> 08:28.455
Then rainy season starts?
It’s part of our country too.

08:28.550 --> 08:32.168
Yes. Don’t worry.

08:34.264 --> 08:35.720
Rainy season will come.

08:36.474 --> 08:38.054
Hurry up and eat.

08:39.436 --> 08:41.597
- Are you excited too?
- About what?

08:42.272 --> 08:44.354
Mom will come
when the rainy season starts.

08:52.449 --> 08:53.154
Ji-ho...

08:53.408 --> 08:54.408
Yes?

08:57.871 --> 08:59.202
Let’s wait and see.

08:59.748 --> 09:01.158
Eat up. You'll be late.

09:01.499 --> 09:04.036
Don’t worry.
Mom will keep her promise.

09:04.461 --> 09:05.826
It’s in the book too!

09:33.364 --> 09:34.319
Your medicine!

09:34.365 --> 09:35.365
Right!

09:40.663 --> 09:41.869
See you later!

09:42.082 --> 09:43.037
Aren’t you hot?

09:43.083 --> 09:45.165
- It might rain
- see you later.

10:09.317 --> 10:10.523
After school...

10:10.527 --> 10:12.392
I'll go to uncle hong—gu.

10:13.655 --> 10:16.021
- Pay attention in class.
- I will.

10:18.451 --> 10:20.737
Go, dad! You're late!

10:30.755 --> 10:31.961
Here you are.

10:32.215 --> 10:33.796
- It's been a while.
- Yes.

10:35.969 --> 10:38.255
- Please come often.
- I will.

10:39.681 --> 10:41.637
How about number 110?

10:41.891 --> 10:42.891
Here you go.

10:48.231 --> 10:50.062
Thanks for the coffee.

10:50.108 --> 10:51.108
Sure.

10:58.283 --> 10:59.283
Wait...

11:01.661 --> 11:02.661
Here.

11:04.164 --> 11:05.164
Pardon?

11:05.957 --> 11:07.663
Your buttons...

11:16.759 --> 11:18.590
Hyun-jung? Coffee.

11:19.721 --> 11:20.927
I had some already.

11:24.058 --> 11:25.514
Did you clean in the morning?

11:26.144 --> 11:27.930
Yes, I cleaned everything.

11:28.479 --> 11:29.479
Good job!

11:36.321 --> 11:39.905
One, two, three, four!

11:39.908 --> 11:43.116
One, two, three, four!

11:43.161 --> 11:44.992
- Look at him!
- He’s handsome!

11:48.833 --> 11:50.323
What are you doing?

11:50.668 --> 11:51.668
Hurry up!

11:51.836 --> 11:55.249
Why are you afraid of
getting in the water?

11:55.506 --> 11:59.624
Why work here
if you're so scared of water?

12:03.348 --> 12:05.179
Hong-gu bakery

12:35.797 --> 12:36.797
not again.

12:37.674 --> 12:39.130
Why the long face?

12:42.720 --> 12:43.835
What happened at school?

12:46.349 --> 12:47.349
Nothing.

12:52.230 --> 12:53.436
Tell me what's wrong.

12:54.732 --> 12:57.189
Dad can’t run, can he?

12:58.152 --> 13:00.518
Why can’t he do so many things?

13:01.239 --> 13:02.239
Going through puberty?

13:02.323 --> 13:03.403
What's that?

13:03.616 --> 13:04.616
Forget it.

13:05.285 --> 13:07.901
Well, your dad is...

13:08.454 --> 13:11.696
You know the lights that turn on
automatically when you pass by?

13:11.791 --> 13:14.077
There's one at our front door.

13:14.252 --> 13:15.332
How does it turn on?

13:15.503 --> 13:17.744
If I move under it.

13:17.797 --> 13:18.797
Right.

13:19.340 --> 13:21.922
Does it turn on
if people don’t pass by it?

13:22.093 --> 13:23.093
It does.

13:23.845 --> 13:25.005
- It does?
- Yup.

13:25.179 --> 13:28.546
It turns on if a fly or the wind
passes under it.

13:28.975 --> 13:30.966
Why's the light like its owner?

13:31.644 --> 13:32.644
Anyway,

13:33.146 --> 13:36.730
if it goes on and off all the time,
what will happen?

13:37.066 --> 13:38.066
It’s broken.

13:38.568 --> 13:39.648
It’s broken already?

13:39.902 --> 13:40.231
Yup.

13:40.570 --> 13:45.360
If you're dad works hard
all the time, he’ll break down too.

13:45.491 --> 13:45.980
I guess.

13:46.200 --> 13:47.781
So, he can’t do everything.

13:48.077 --> 13:50.693
That's why he can’t run?

13:51.539 --> 13:52.539
It’s too hard.

13:53.583 --> 13:54.823
What about driving?

13:55.668 --> 13:57.033
What if he gets in an accident?

13:57.670 --> 13:58.750
And movie theaters?

13:58.838 --> 14:01.045
There’s lots to watch on TV.

14:04.344 --> 14:06.005
But why ask about running?

14:06.346 --> 14:09.338
I'm the class rep
for the relay race.

14:09.432 --> 14:12.094
Way to go, kid!

14:12.143 --> 14:13.929
We have to run with our dads.

14:15.772 --> 14:18.309
You've got me! Don’t worry!

14:18.358 --> 14:21.850
But your legs are short.

14:22.028 --> 14:23.028
Ji—ho!

14:24.405 --> 14:25.815
You got my legs all wrong!

14:26.074 --> 14:27.074
Come here.

14:30.328 --> 14:30.783
Here.

14:31.329 --> 14:32.409
Touch right there.

14:33.790 --> 14:35.746
- Feel that bone?
- Yes!

14:36.250 --> 14:38.241
Most people’s legs stop there.

14:40.755 --> 14:41.835
Now, touch mine.

14:43.424 --> 14:45.085
I can’t feel it!

14:45.176 --> 14:47.337
Know why you can’t feel
my leg bones?

14:47.804 --> 14:48.418
No.

14:48.638 --> 14:50.299
My legs don’t stop there!

14:50.640 --> 14:52.130
My legs go up to here!

14:52.308 --> 14:52.842
Like what?

14:52.975 --> 14:53.760
Penguins!

14:53.935 --> 14:56.347
Then think I'll be fast or not
with these long legs?

14:56.354 --> 14:58.936
- Totally fast!
- You got it!

14:58.981 --> 14:59.981
Let’s win!

15:02.151 --> 15:03.151
Dad!

15:06.322 --> 15:07.732
Why do you look so happy?

15:07.740 --> 15:11.073
Uncle hong—-gu will run
in the relay race with me.

15:11.119 --> 15:12.484
- Relay race?
- Yes!

15:12.662 --> 15:14.823
We're supposed to run
with our dads,

15:14.831 --> 15:18.164
but uncle Hong-gu says he’s fast
because of his super long legs.

15:22.296 --> 15:24.378
Really? That's great.

15:26.175 --> 15:28.757
Bye uncle Hong-gu!
Go penguin!

15:28.803 --> 15:29.803
Go!

15:33.266 --> 15:34.266
Thanks, pal.

15:34.350 --> 15:35.350
No problem.

15:36.018 --> 15:39.135
One of my customers
is a really classy lady.

15:39.188 --> 15:40.188
See ya.

15:41.023 --> 15:42.559
Don’t be shy, pall

15:53.077 --> 15:55.068
blue team wins/

15:57.206 --> 15:58.491
thanks for your help.

15:59.459 --> 16:01.165
Don’t worry. Have fun.

16:01.377 --> 16:02.377
Thank you.

16:04.130 --> 16:05.130
Hey, jeong!

16:08.301 --> 16:08.881
Come here.

16:09.177 --> 16:11.384
We got many complaints.

16:11.429 --> 16:15.263
Members say it's dark
and the light is flashing.

16:15.308 --> 16:18.641
I'd change it,
but I'm afraid of heights.

16:18.644 --> 16:20.930
I can’t even change my light bulbs.

16:21.689 --> 16:23.520
Could you hurry it up?

16:23.566 --> 16:24.566
Your son must be waiting.

16:25.151 --> 16:27.483
Isn't there a race every year?

16:28.112 --> 16:29.568
You can go next year, right?

16:29.739 --> 16:30.899
Listen up.

16:31.282 --> 16:33.113
When I get the Baton
and start running,

16:33.159 --> 16:35.525
it takes me about 3 seconds
to reach full speed.

16:35.745 --> 16:38.111
Get it? You hear me?

16:38.122 --> 16:38.907
So I'll...

16:38.915 --> 16:39.915
Jeong ji-ho!

16:47.924 --> 16:50.506
Wow! His legs are really long!

16:51.093 --> 16:52.378
See? I told you!

16:54.555 --> 16:55.555
Still, he can't.

17:02.146 --> 17:03.682
Why's it so small?

17:08.027 --> 17:09.392
Give me the shirt.

17:10.112 --> 17:11.112
Why?

17:11.280 --> 17:12.520
Hurry up.

17:13.324 --> 17:14.358
What's with you?

17:14.617 --> 17:16.858
You're not my dad.

17:16.911 --> 17:24.534
Next up is the family relay run.
Participants, take your positions.

17:24.877 --> 17:26.867
Your attention, please.

17:27.296 --> 17:35.214
Next up is the family relay run.
Participants, take your positions.

17:40.059 --> 17:40.718
Daddy!

17:40.851 --> 17:43.718
Son? I can just jog, right?

17:43.771 --> 17:45.727
Sure! I'll run fast!

17:47.567 --> 17:49.432
Let’s go white team!

17:49.485 --> 17:51.350
Let’s go blue team!

18:03.457 --> 18:05.072
Hurry! Faster!

18:05.668 --> 18:06.953
Hurry!!

18:14.385 --> 18:16.091
Last runners get ready!

18:26.397 --> 18:27.397
Ji—ho!

18:30.693 --> 18:32.149
That's it! Go ji-ho!

18:36.574 --> 18:37.574
Go! Go! Go!

18:45.583 --> 18:49.917
Go blue team!

19:40.221 --> 19:42.007
Get up, mister!

19:42.807 --> 19:43.807
Dad!

20:02.993 --> 20:05.359
- I must've embarrassed you.
- No way!

20:09.792 --> 20:10.792
Dad?

20:14.922 --> 20:18.164
You'll never leave me, will you?

20:24.306 --> 20:28.640
I'm not going anywhere
without you.

20:28.686 --> 20:30.893
- Promise?
- Of course!

20:34.525 --> 20:36.186
I swear on cloudland.

20:36.235 --> 20:37.235
Okay!

20:43.117 --> 20:44.117
I'll carry you.

20:44.660 --> 20:46.116
But you must be tired.

20:46.704 --> 20:49.571
I want to carry my son.
Get on.

20:52.710 --> 20:53.825
Let's gol!

20:56.380 --> 20:57.540
Dad?

20:57.840 --> 20:58.840
What?

20:59.091 --> 21:02.675
Let's wash our blankets
when we go home.

21:03.929 --> 21:04.929
Why?

21:05.222 --> 21:07.588
Uncle Hong-gu said
then it'll rain.

21:08.184 --> 21:10.049
- Really?
- Yup!

21:10.728 --> 21:13.219
- Then let's go home faster.
- Okay!

21:13.731 --> 21:15.187
- Hold tight!
- Okay.

21:17.276 --> 21:18.482
Let's fly!

21:22.740 --> 21:24.105
What are you looking for?

21:24.700 --> 21:25.780
A four-lear clover.

21:25.868 --> 21:31.238
You said if we find 10 of them,
a wish will come true.

21:31.248 --> 21:32.784
What’s your wish ji-ho?

21:34.084 --> 21:35.164
For you to be healthy.

21:37.880 --> 21:40.872
Thanks honey.
Mommy will be healthy.

21:41.175 --> 21:43.962
- Promise?
- Promise!

22:18.629 --> 22:19.629
Dad!

22:22.883 --> 22:24.419
Dad! It's raining!

22:24.510 --> 22:25.545
What?

22:25.678 --> 22:27.384
Let's go see mom!

22:28.389 --> 22:29.389
Ji—ho!

22:29.932 --> 22:30.932
Ji—ho!

22:31.016 --> 22:32.756
You'll catch a cold! Wait!

22:34.562 --> 22:35.562
Ji—ho!

22:57.001 --> 22:58.001
Mom!

23:00.504 --> 23:01.504
Mommy!

23:03.090 --> 23:04.705
Mom! Where are you?

23:09.972 --> 23:13.055
That's weird. Where's mom?

23:13.851 --> 23:16.217
She’s not here yet?

23:28.782 --> 23:29.782
Wanna go now?

23:30.284 --> 23:31.774
No! I'm not leaving.

23:34.288 --> 23:35.619
You'll catch a cold.

23:36.790 --> 23:38.200
I'm not going!

23:41.837 --> 23:44.920
Something must've kept her
from coming today.

23:45.549 --> 23:46.834
Let's come next time.

23:48.135 --> 23:52.003
No! Mom said she'll come
with the rain!

23:54.266 --> 23:55.631
Let's go home.

23:55.726 --> 23:58.934
No! She said she’ll come today!

23:59.229 --> 24:05.225
Put me down! Stop it!

24:25.422 --> 24:26.422
What's that?

24:31.178 --> 24:32.178
It’s mom!

24:36.016 --> 24:38.428
Why? I want to go to mom!

24:38.811 --> 24:41.644
You wait right here.
I'll go check first.

24:41.897 --> 24:42.897
No!

24:43.190 --> 24:44.190
Jeong ji-ho!

24:53.409 --> 24:55.365
Stay back!

25:03.335 --> 25:05.326
It’s mom, right?

25:05.921 --> 25:06.921
Wait.

25:07.923 --> 25:10.414
Calm down. Relax

25:11.301 --> 25:12.507
she could be a ghost.

25:12.720 --> 25:14.426
Who cares? She’s mom.

25:16.473 --> 25:17.588
Right.

25:18.017 --> 25:19.017
Mom!

25:19.601 --> 25:20.601
Ji—ho!

25:21.395 --> 25:22.395
Mommy!

25:22.521 --> 25:23.727
No! Don’t touch her!

25:23.731 --> 25:25.096
- Mom!
- No!

25:25.482 --> 25:26.767
- Mom!
- Watch out! Stop!

25:27.443 --> 25:29.604
- Ji-ho!
- Mom! Wake up!

25:41.665 --> 25:43.371
See? It’s mom!

25:45.961 --> 25:46.961
Who are you?

25:47.921 --> 25:51.834
Mom? Don’t you remember?
It's me, ji-ho.

25:52.926 --> 25:53.926
Mom?

25:54.178 --> 25:55.178
I'm your mom?

25:55.637 --> 25:57.673
Why don’t you know me?

25:57.723 --> 26:01.466
You said you'll come back
from cloudland when it rains.

26:02.019 --> 26:03.509
What does that mean?

26:04.438 --> 26:07.726
Dad! Explain it to her! Come on!

26:10.861 --> 26:11.941
It hurts.

26:12.488 --> 26:17.528
Get up!
I'll show you at home. Come on!

26:17.618 --> 26:18.618
Wait.

26:18.744 --> 26:20.484
- Hurry!
- Let's go home.

26:34.426 --> 26:35.586
This is you, mom.

26:35.844 --> 26:38.210
You and me. See?

26:43.519 --> 26:44.519
There’s more!

26:56.448 --> 26:57.233
Tadal

26:57.282 --> 26:58.146
welcome back mom!

26:58.200 --> 27:00.486
I made this for your return.

27:01.787 --> 27:02.787
Ji—ho!

27:04.414 --> 27:07.577
I left your things as they are.

27:07.584 --> 27:09.996
Go change and get comfortable.

27:10.003 --> 27:12.460
- Don’t you need to pee?
- No.

27:12.506 --> 27:15.623
- You should pee. Let's go!
- I don’t have to!

27:19.054 --> 27:22.091
Why doesn’t mom
remember anything?

27:23.517 --> 27:26.509
Maybe she hit her head
on the way from cloudland?

27:27.146 --> 27:29.683
I don’t think
she knows that either.

27:30.190 --> 27:30.645
What?

27:31.108 --> 27:32.108
That she...

27:32.359 --> 27:33.474
Went to cloudland.

27:35.279 --> 27:36.279
Oh really?

27:40.117 --> 27:43.154
Ji-ho? Let’s keep this a secret.

27:43.745 --> 27:44.359
Why?

27:44.663 --> 27:47.700
What if she gets shocked
and leaves?

27:48.083 --> 27:49.914
Don’t ever say
she'll leave again.

27:49.918 --> 27:54.708
Let's pretend
we lived together all along.

27:54.756 --> 27:57.873
And don’t tell anyone else.
Understand?

27:59.887 --> 28:03.800
If we help her,
mom will get her memory back.

28:04.183 --> 28:05.183
Okay?

28:10.272 --> 28:12.604
Doesn't mom look
a lot healthier?

28:12.733 --> 28:13.813
Yes! And prettier!

28:13.859 --> 28:15.520
Mom's always been pretty.

28:16.862 --> 28:17.862
Let's go.

28:18.906 --> 28:19.906
Excuse me?

28:20.616 --> 28:24.700
Did I really live here?

28:25.120 --> 28:26.951
Yes, you lived here.

28:27.998 --> 28:29.704
- Right?
- Right!

28:29.958 --> 28:36.170
But you mentioned cloudland
and looked happy to see me.

28:36.840 --> 28:38.080
You welcomed me.

28:38.842 --> 28:40.753
And you said you left
my things as they are.

28:42.512 --> 28:44.969
I let the house
get messy like this?

28:51.063 --> 28:52.063
Well...

28:54.900 --> 28:56.356
You were... ah...

28:57.110 --> 28:58.110
Sick!

28:59.196 --> 28:59.855
I was?

29:00.072 --> 29:00.686
That's right!

29:00.906 --> 29:03.613
You were sick and stayed
in the hospital.

29:03.659 --> 29:04.659
Cloudland hospital!

29:06.578 --> 29:07.784
Cloudland...

29:09.081 --> 29:11.538
Why was I in the tunnel
and not the hospital?

29:12.668 --> 29:14.158
You got cured yesterday!

29:17.172 --> 29:20.414
Right! You came home yesterday.

29:20.592 --> 29:22.207
We played hide-and-seek!

29:23.387 --> 29:24.502
Hide-and-seek?

29:25.889 --> 29:28.801
You love playing that.
You're really good.

29:28.809 --> 29:29.389
Right ji-ho?

29:29.559 --> 29:31.049
