- Shut up!

44:31.210 --> 44:32.325
You have a crush!

44:32.587 --> 44:33.587
Stop!

44:37.049 --> 44:38.084
You didn’t write yet.

44:44.599 --> 44:45.599
Me?

44:46.350 --> 44:47.350
Right.

44:49.353 --> 44:52.186
- Woo-Jin? Got a pen?
