52:03.787 --> 52:07.780
Didn't you read
a book called 'Norwegian forest’?

52:08.459 --> 52:09.459
What?

52:14.965 --> 52:16.705
That's just a novel.

52:17.176 --> 52:19.383
It has nothing to do with Norway.

52:23.057 --> 52:24.388
Actually,

52:24.767 --> 52:28.601
